title: Detective Conan Movie 16: The Eleventh Striker
title_jp: 劇場版　名探偵コナン　11人目のストライカー
synopsis: After an interaction with J-League professional players, Conan and co watches the big match between Tokyo Spirits and Gamba Osaka, only to find out that a bomb has been planted in the stadium. It is now up to Conan once again to foil the culprit's plans and reveal his/her true identity.
